 bringing the AV program sensor total to 51. AV CD 4 requirements validated in FY 2021. Continued deployment of Pre-Planned Product Improvement (P3I) Green Falcon version 3 (GFv3) and Tech Refresh of
 GFv2 adds enhanced capabilities that pace the threat.
